---
title: "Ep 362: The Best and Worst of 2024!"
publishDate: "2024-12-27"
category: "major-issues"
episodeNumber: 362
spotifyUrl: "https://comicbookclique.podbean.com/e/ep-362-the-best-and-worst-of-2024/"
