In this year-end special of the Major Issues Podcast, the hosts take a deep dive into 2025, reviewing the highs and lows of the year in entertainment. From the gritty, underworld drama of The Penguin to the unlimited laughs of Deadpool and Wolverine, they break down the standout moments and unexpected surprises. But it's not all praise – the hosts also dish out their thoughts on flawed films like Joker: Folie à Deux and Madame Web, exploring what worked, what didn’t, and how these stories stacked up to the hype. Tune in for a candid discussion of the best and worst of 2025 and get ready for a lively, spoiler-filled conversation that looks back at the year that was. Don't miss it!

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

